		<title>狗狗也有樣學樣？米克斯犬與主人「互相打鬧」讓網友笑翻 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/12/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b9%9f%e6%9c%89%e6%a8%a3%e5%ad%b8%e6%a8%a3%ef%bc%9f%e7%b1%b3%e5%85%8b%e6%96%af%e7%8a%ac%e8%88%87%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%e3%80%8c%e4%ba%92%e7%9b%b8%e6%89%93%e9%ac%a7%e3%80%8d%e8%ae%93/</link>
		
