		<title>中美貿易休戰見效 中國宣布解除部分關鍵礦產出口禁令</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/10/%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e4%bc%91%e6%88%b0%e8%a6%8b%e6%95%88-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%ae%a3%e5%b8%83%e8%a7%a3%e9%99%a4%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e9%97%9c%e9%8d%b5%e7%a4%a6%e7%94%a2%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 10 Nov 2025 07:52:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[中國]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新聞]]></category>
